---
import Sparkles from "../icon/Sparkles.astro"
import Github from "../icon/Github.astro"
import Mail from "../icon/Mail.astro"

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear()
---
<footer class="py-16 px-4 border-t border-[#7d64c7]/10">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-12">
      {/* Logo and description */}
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-[#b69df1] flex items-center justify-center">
            <Sparkles class="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Prompts Cake</span>
        </div>

        <p class="text-[#a495c6] max-w-md leading-relaxed">
          La extensión de Chrome que revoluciona tu flujo de trabajo con IA. Organiza, guarda y reutiliza prompts
          como un profesional.
        </p>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="#"
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#2f2546]/50 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#2f2546] transition-colors"
          >
            <Github class="w-5 h-5 text-[#7d64c7]" />
          </a>
          <a
            href="#"
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#2f2546]/50 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#2f2546] transition-colors"
          >
            <Mail class="w-5 h-5 text-[#7d64c7]" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Product links */}
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Producto</h4>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <a href="#" class="block text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Características
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Precios
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Roadmap
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Changelog
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Support links */}
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Soporte</h4>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <a href="#" class="block text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Documentación
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Guías
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            FAQ
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Contacto
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Bottom section */}
    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-[#7d64c7]/10">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-6 text-sm text-[#7d64c7] text-center">
          <span>© {currentYear} Prompts Cake. Todos los derechos reservados.</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm">
          <a href="#" class="text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Términos
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Privacidad
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="text-[#a495c6] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Cookies
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <p class="text-[#7d64c7] text-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          Hecho con ♥ para la comunidad de IA
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>